org.teatrove.trove.util.tq
Class TransactionQueueEvent

java.lang.Object
  java.util.EventObject
      org.teatrove.trove.util.tq.TransactionQueueEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TransactionQueueEvent
extends EventObject

An event that contains information from a TransactionQueue. TransactionQueueEvents can be received by implementing a TransactionQueueListener.

Author:
Brian S O'Neill

public long getStageDuration()
